    "195717736": {
      "title": "A fast triangle-triangle intersection test",
      "abstract": "Abstract This paper presents a method, along with some optimizations, for computing whether or not two triangles intersect. The code, which is shown to be fast, can be used, for example, in collision detection algorithms."
